      "body": "> Additionally, the effectiveness of this alternative could be undermined when using https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/30206 build profiles for macOS targets.\n\nI don't understand this concern, can you ellaborate on this a bit? Are you proposing to remove the native packages entirely? If not, would we instruct the guix depends build step to skip the native packages? I'm guessing most of the speedup comes from the native qt build? Might there be some more stuff we can skip on it?",
